          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/913.-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>pancetta</strong> is crispy, add the <strong>diced </strong><strong>onion </strong>to the pan with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook over a medium heat for 3-4 min or until soft </p>\n<p>Once soft, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/913.-Step-3-x200.jpg",
