    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock cube</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span> in 650ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.1L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>chicken stock </strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
