    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong>, <strong>conchiglie</strong>,<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[3 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to the pan</p>\n<p>Cover with a lid and cook over a medium heat for 12-14 min or until the <strong>conchiglie</strong> is cooked</p>",
      "order": 5,
